{"tid":1324921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家聽我講唔好搞元朗","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T00:33:35.000Z","uid":279481,"like":40,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0200a5609b299d0d498c3df4d2b8a1d4795b3a","tid":1324921,"uid":279481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"唔好鬧我p牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知好多巴打都有股熱誠出去幫手<br />\n但搞元朗對之後真係<span style=\"color: red;\">弊多於利</span><br />\n元朗啲牛屎佬有幾撚惡真係無見過都聽過<br />\n警犬都驚佢哋三分啦<br />\n講開片佢哋真係唔撚驚<br />\n就算今次贏左<br />\n佢哋就出嚟報仇/搞事？<br />\n而且只會令好多巴打受傷<br />\n令之後繼續抗爭嘅人數變少<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時係益左政府同啲警犬啊！！</span></span><br />\n大家唔好忘記為左啲咩而行出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">係五大訴求啊！！！</span></span><br />\n革命道路仲有好長<br />\n千奇唔好衰一時衝動啊！！！<br />\n香港仲要靠我哋<br />\n所以求下大家冷靜啲諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b7df3b324272527a4146a2c79388d1e0515587","tid":1324921,"uid":279481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2675dd1e8a235e58a8b819f665d4cbf1ecd82e0c","tid":1324921,"uid":279481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f063ca66afadec15fc7a1067f84d16855c2df22d","tid":1324921,"uid":279481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b9b06569af03f76ea4b51313d894e813c49eca6","tid":1324921,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"Push，721港島見"},{"pid":"f799aec1b6171fe6f598d26e1d704a89844993e0","tid":1324921,"uid":264717,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedB